FBIS3-37752 "drsov036_s_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 Georgia Parliament Postpones Government Confirmation LD2202171894 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1530 GMT 22 Feb 94 LD2202171894 Tbilisi IBERIA Language: Georgian Article Type:BFN [Text] Tbilisi, 22 Feb -- IBERIA reports that at a meeting of the Georgian parliament today, Head of State Eduard Shevardnadze said that, owing to a grave energy crisis, the confirmation of the composition of the acting government should be postponed until 15 March. The majority of parliamentarians, including those from opposition factions, supported this proposal.
